                                GenomeInfo genome)
        Updates a genomeInfo object in both temporal and persistent databases
        Parameters:
        username: - Owner of the target population that has the chosen genomeInfo object
        populationID: - Identifier of the target population
        genome: - GenomeInfo object The persistent database will be updated only if populationID is > 0
